## ğŸ§­ PHASE 4: **Movement & Editing Commands (G5)**

### ğŸ“Œ Goal

Implement all basic editor actions

### ğŸ“Œ Actions to Handle

| Action       | Trigger Key | Effect                    |
| ------------ | ----------- | ------------------------- |
| Move left    | â†           | `cursor.col -= 1`         |
| Move right   | â†’           | `cursor.col += 1`         |
| Move up/down | â†‘ / â†“       | `cursor.row Â±= 1`         |
| Backspace    | âŒ«           | Delete char before cursor |
| Delete       | Del         | Delete char at cursor     |
| Insert char  | any key     | Insert at cursor          |
| Enter        | â           | Split line                |

### âœ… Structures to Support

* Cursor object with row/col
* Text buffer with lines
* Functions:

  * `insert_char(c)`
  * `delete_before_cursor()`
  * `delete_at_cursor()`
