## ğŸ“˜ Summary â€” Ordered Learning Milestones

| Phase | Task                         | Key Data Structure or Algo  |
| ----- | ---------------------------- | --------------------------- |
| 1     | Read raw keystrokes          | `msvcrt.getch()`            |
| 2     | Build buffer + cursor system | Rope, Gap Buffer, or List   |
